8`,hint:"Python的交互式模式非常适合进行快速计算"}],prerequisites:["lesson_1_1"],tags:["入门","print","基础"]},Th={id:"lesson_3_1",title:"Python语法基础",description:"了解Python的基本语法规则",difficulty:"beginner",estimatedTime:15,chapter:3,order:1,pseudoCode:`
